rederick Loewe Theatre and the Kimmel  Center&#39;s 3rd floor Market Place and 4th floor Eisner & Lubin  Auditorium. Banners will serve as guides while you stroll down Grad  Alley enjoying the entertainment as well as jugglers, an illusionist,  Lady Liberty and more. Do no leave without trying your luck on Arcade  Alley. Snacks are available while taking in the sights and  entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Guests will enjoy a number of entertainment venues including &lt;strong&gt;NYU Dance Fever on Gould Plaza,&lt;/strong&gt; where you can dance the night away or just relax to the sounds of DJ Marcus;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;NYU Jazz Caf&eacute; in the Eisner & Lubin Auditorium&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring the NYU Steinhardt Jazz Orchestra with a number of special guest performances; &lt;strong&gt;NYU Pep Band on LaGuardia Place&lt;/strong&gt; and much more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grad Alley takes place rain or shine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information on Grad Alley, copy & paste the URL below to your web browser:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Tue, 19 May 2015 17:00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"37128\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:259;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"\n			\n			\n			\n			\n            \n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"(5/19/15) 2015 Barristers&amp;#39; Ball\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://its.law.nyu.edu/eventcalendar/index.cfm?fuseaction=main.detail&id=34969\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:651:\"&lt;p&gt;Graduating J.D.&#39;s, LL.M.&#39;s, J.S.D.&#39;s, and guests are cordially invited to this annual celebration for graduating students. The Barristers&#39; Ball is the Law School&#39;s opportunity to acknowledge you in an intimate and elegant setting for the contributions you have made to our community. Semi-Formal Attire. More details and ticket information can be found on the Student Affairs website.&lt;a title=\"Barristers&#39; Ball\" href=\"http://www.law.nyu.edu/studentaffairs/convocation/barristersball\" target=\"_blank\"&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Access to this event is by invitation only.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Tue, 19 May 2015 20:00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"34969\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:260;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"\n			\n			\n			\n			\n            \n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"(5/20/15) All University Commencement 2015\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://its.law.nyu.edu/eventcalendar/index.cfm?fuseaction=main.detail&id=32377\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i: