\">NYC DOE Home</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://schools.nyc.gov/ChoicesEnrollment/Elementary/default.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Elementary School Choices and Enrollment</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://schools.nyc.gov/ChoicesEnrollment/PreK/default.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Pre K Choices and Enrollment</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://schools.nyc.gov/ChoicesEnrollment/Middle/default.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Middle Schools Choices and Enrollment</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://schools.nyc.gov/Accountability/resources/testing/default.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Testing Info</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://arisparentlink.org/parentlink\" target=\"_blank\">ARIS (Achievement Reporting and Innovation System) PARENT LINK</a>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.opt-osfns.org/schoolfood/public1/menu_select.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">School Food Menu Page</a>','Resources','','publish','open','open','','resources','','','2012-09-26 21:45:03','2012-09-26 21:45:03','',344,'http://childrensworkshopschool.org/?page_id=363',0,'page','',0),(374,1,'2012-09-26 21:52:54','2012-09-26 21:52:54','<a href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/maria2.jpg\">\n</a><a href=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/maria2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone\" style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/maria2.jpg\" alt=\"maria\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"20\" /></a><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong><span class=\"BoldIntroText_AdminGold\">Principal: Maria Velez-Clarke</span></strong></span>\n\nPlease read the <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/schoolbook/2011/10/06/maria-velez-clarke-how-do-we-catch-the-b-train/\" target=\"_blank\">New York Times Schoolbook interview.</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n<img style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/dorothy.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"20\" /><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong><span class=\"BoldIntroText_AdminGold\">Parent Coordinator: Dorothy Cantwell</span></strong></span>\n\nI am the liaison between parents and the school administration, staff members and teachers. You can find me in the Main Office on the second floor or the Library on the 4th floor. I am always available to talk to parents about any concerns, questions or suggestions they may have. I will be the one sending out important emails to keep you updated on school information. I will be updating the school calendars on the website. <a href=\"mailto:ptcoordinator@childrensworkshopschool.org\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">ptcoordinator{at}childrensworkshopschool.org</a> or <a rel=\"nofollow\">212.614.9531</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n<img style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"http://childrensworkshopschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/joyce.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"20\" /><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong><span class=\"BoldIntroText_AdminGold\">School Secretary: Joyce Borden</span></strong></span>\n\nI am the School Secretary, and you can find me in the Main Office on the second floor. As the school secretary I wear many hats. I coordinate and handle the following activities and events: admissions; school tours; school photos; spring photos; schedule meetings with the principal. I co-chair the newly formed Garden Committee, and I also Chair the School Clubs Afterschool Program. You will see me every afternoon in the lobby. You can contact me at 212.614.9531 x2091. or at<a href=\"mailto:joyce@childrensworkshopschool.org\" target=\"_blank\"> joyce{at}childrensworkshopschool.org</a>','Administration','','publish','open','open','','administration','','','2012-09-26 21:52:54','2012-09-26 21:52:54','',189,'http://childrensworkshopschool.org/?page_id=374',0,'page','',0),(391,1,'2012-09-27 06:01:52','2012-09-27 06:01:52','<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"170\"><a title=\"ANNOUNCEMENTS\" href=\