were able to go for five days.  Sadly, that annual $10,000 gift has ended, leaving Children’s Workshop with the prospect of a truncated 2-day farm trip for this year’s group of 4th graders.  We are hoping to make up that shortfall, but it’s a struggle for a small, progressive public school on the Lower East Side.  To that end, we are reaching out to family and friends, and their families and friends, to help us meet our goal.  Won’t you help us continue our school’s tradition?\r\n\r\nWe raised a whopping 75% of the goal of $10K to fund the farm trip for the 4th graders using the <a href=\"http://www.gofundme.com/h9pqgo\">GoFundMe site</a><a href=\"http://www.gofundme.com/h9pqgo\"> (http://www.gofundme.com/h9pqgo) </a>. Please spread the word! Every bit helps.','UPDATED! We raised 100% of the goal of $10,000 for the 4th Grade Farm Trip','','inherit','open','open','','1476-revision-v1','','','2015-01-15 22:59:28','2015-01-16 03:59:28','',1476,'http://cws.elab.io/1476-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1818,1,'2015-01-15 23:06:16','2015-01-16 04:06:16','','10940441_10205919416010356_6600437804005915868_n','','inherit','open','open','','10940441_10205919416010356_6600437804005915868_n','','','2015-01-15 23:06:16','2015-01-16 04:06:16','',0,'http://cws.elab.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10940441_10205919416010356_6600437804005915868_n.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1820,1,'2015-01-16 00:47:21','2015-01-16 05:47:21','','cwsfav','','inherit','open','open','','cwsfav','','','2015-01-16 00:47:21','2015-01-16 05:47:21','',0,'http://cws.elab.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/cwsfav.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1823,1,'2015-01-16 01:48:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2015-01-16 01:48:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://cws.elab.io/?p=1823',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1858,1,'2015-02-24 19:02:21','2015-02-25 00:02:21','The Children\'s Workshop School, founded in 1993, is a progressive public elementary school located on the East Vi